      "title": "PNR ALERT: Pentair Investigated for Securities Fraud Violations by Block & Leviton",
      "summary": "Block & Leviton is investigating Pentair (NYSE: PNR) for potential securities law violations related to misleading statements about Pool channel inventory health. After guiding to 1% Q2 growth in April 2026, Pentair pre-announced a 17% year-over-year sales decline and slashed full-year outlook, citing unexpected inventory destocking that would reduce Pool sales by ~$250 million. The company's CFO also departed days before the warning. Investors who lost money may be eligible to recover losses.",
